OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a mixture of sunny then clear
OL,7,Finterludes and a few showers, these
OL,8,Fshowers more concentrated in the
OL,9,FNorthwest and Isles, fewer in south
OL,10,Fand east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA mostly dry day with bright
OL,13,Fspells the best sunshine around the
OL,14,Fcoasts. Still the odd passing shower,
OL,15,Fmost likely in the Northwest and the
OL,16,FIsles. Rather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
