OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloud
OL,6,Fwith showery rain soon spreading south
OL,7,Fon Sunday. Sunny spells on Monday
OL,8,Fmorning then some light rain later.
OL,9,FTuesday breezy with showers and sunny
OL,10,Fintervals.
